sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Telemetry Pipeline
    participant Raw as S3 Raw
    participant Catalog as Glue Catalog
    participant Query as Athena
    participant Results as S3 Query Results

    App->>Raw: Write telemetry objects
    Catalog->>Raw: Register metadata / partitions
    Query->>Catalog: Resolve schema
    Query->>Raw: Scan matching partitions
    Query->>Results: Store query output